s-sarisa.aspx"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Times; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.bbsrc.ac.uk/funding/opportunities/2013/2013-gfs-sarisa.aspx</span></a><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Times; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn10"></a><a href="#_ftnref10">[10]</a><span style="font-family:Times; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.isis.stfc.ac.uk/science/energy/capturing-a-cleaner-future13465.html"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Times; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">htt</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Times; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">p://www.isis.stfc.ac.uk/science/energy/capturing-a-cleaner-future13465.html</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn11"></a><a href="#_ftnref11">[11]</a><span style="font-family:Times; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://dbkgroup.org/carbonsequestration/rootsystem.html"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Times; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://dbkgroup.org/carbonsequestration/rootsystem.html</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn12"></a><a href="#_ftnref12">[12]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.bgs.ac.uk/qics/"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">://www.bgs.ac.uk/qics/</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn13"></a><a href="#_ftnref13">[13]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.eco2-project.eu/"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.eco2-project.eu/</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="